Three suspected thugs were last night shot dead in two separate robbery incidents in Parklands and Industrial Area. Police recovered two pistols from the suspects. Read; Cops gun down 7 suspected thugs, say they killed 2 officers in Kibichoi, Kiambu The first incident happened in City Park area where two suspects were shot dead after they were ambushed while robbing residents. A third suspect managed to escape.  And in Industrial Area, a third suspect was killed as he robbed locals. The bodies have been moved to the mortuary Also read: Three thugs killed in Kenol ‘kind, friendly and played with baby’  